    "summary": "In GnuPG through 2.4.8, armor_filter in g10/armor.c has two increments of an index variable where...",
    "details": "In GnuPG before 2.4.9, armor_filter in g10/armor.c has two increments of an index variable where one is intended, leading to an out-of-bounds write for crafted input. (For ExtendedLTS, 2.2.51 and later are fixed versions.)",
